civil laws'''Civil law''' may refer to:* Civil law (common law), a branch of  law which consists of non-criminal law* Civil law (legal system) (or Continental law), any of the various systems or codes of law which are derived from Roman law historically** Civil law (area), a branch of Continental law which is the general part of private law* Municipal law, the domestic law of a stateSee also* Civil (disambiguation)* ''Ius civile'', Latin for "civil law"